data.description:
Assumable FHA loan at 5.75% interest rate to qualified buyers! Nice Burney home just 3 blocks from stores, 1 block from schools, park and neighborhood pool; Home is 3 bedroom 2 baths with attached garage. This home was fully remodeld in 2018 including new siding, windows, doors, flooring, kitchen appliances, cabinets and granite slab countertops in the kitchen and updated bathrooms. Home has
large backyard with pergola covering the patio with large shade trees and is fully fenced with drive thru gates on both ends of yard. Home is equipped with a new furnace/AC package unit and a tankless water heater. Come see this affordable, move-in ready home.
